      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.840 - Ammar al-Sabati narrate from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) that He said:\n\"The area between the hairline and the tip of the nose is considered a place of prostration (masjid), so whatever part of it touches the ground suffices.\""
        ]
